snippet.title: WINONA RYDER Says Amber Heard Is WRONG About Johnny Depp
snippet.description:
Winona Ryder has been confirmed to say that Amber Heard is wrong about Johnny Depp.
This is another win for Johnny Depp in his libel case against the sun and his former wife Amber Heard who has accused Johnny Depp of some very serious crimes.
Johnny Depp's ex-partner Winona Ryder has said it is "impossible to believe" allegations from his former wife Amber Heard that he was violent.
